Type: Package
Package: distiller
Title: Distill EPHT Data Down to XML
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Senetcky", , "asenetcky@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-3730-5397"))
Description: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention's (CDC) Environmental
    Public Health Tracking Network (EPHT) data 
    submission process has a lot documentation.  Much of it
    is buried and out of date, making it difficult for new users to
    decipher the exact specifications of the data submissions' XML.
    `distiller` makes it easier to create the intended XML data products.
